Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.05,0:01:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄當忍者吧 綱手的通告
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.75,0:01:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得漂亮 赤丸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.05,0:02:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全中了 空中動態標記
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.75,0:02:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是空翻三周
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.15,0:02:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要命中目標哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.55,0:02:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這難道也叫散步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.85,0:02:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 絕對不是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.95,0:02:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就不能靜下心來收集蟲子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.45,0:02:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.95,0:02:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三人各有所長 各有所好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.75,0:02:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛田 你也能找到喜歡的就好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.55,0:02:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也對呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.75,0:02:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.95,0:02:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有事的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.25,0:02:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的提示都在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.25,0:02:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想出最快到達目的地的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.75,0:02:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.55,0:03:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同學們 非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的課就上到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.05,0:03:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.05,0:03:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.94,0:03:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑板上的就作為家庭作業了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.25,0:03:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用上體術課真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.55,0:03:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是現在才上午啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.55,0:03:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就放學了 真不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.55,0:03:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嗎這麼認真嘛 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.43,0:03:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是啊 木葉丸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉丸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.55,0:04:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉丸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.35,0:04:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們打算把爺爺的東西怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.47,0:04:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.85,0:04:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是爺爺的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.75,0:04:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算拿到哪裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.25,0:04:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嗎 現在沒用了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.15,0:04:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算將它放到其他地方去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.45,0:04:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒用了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.55,0:04:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們就這麼隨便處理爺爺的遺物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.35,0:04:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡將要成為第五代的辦公室
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.25,0:04:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第五代
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.75,0:04:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 下一任火影大人要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.35,0:04:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村裡的人也總算放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.95,0:04:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說那位火影不喜歡香煙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.85,0:04:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼第五代嘛 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.36,0:04:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也未免太快了點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.75,0:04:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今為止不都是靠我爺爺撐著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.85,0:05:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.15,0:05:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這裡幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.75,0:05:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這應該是我問你的才對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.65,0:05:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個好色小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.25,0:05:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說一遍試試
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.25,0:05:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還想讓我再說一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.25,0:05:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好色小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.15,0:05:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再叫我好色小鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.05,0:05:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.45,0:05:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長老們都等著呢 得抓緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.95,0:05:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.15,0:05:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後要注意點哦 小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.25,0:05:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您自己也要自覺一點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.13,0:05:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挨罵的總是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.85,0:06:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是小朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.25,0:06:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.75,0:06:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.65,0:06:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.65,0:06:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉丸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.95,0:06:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.27,0:06:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.12,0:06:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有看到一個胸部很大的可怕婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.75,0:06:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 應該是大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.45,0:06:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.45,0:06:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙到底是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.45,0:06:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.95,0:06:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.75,0:06:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.80,0:06:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快點去醫院就來不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.95,0:06:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位大姐可是很厲害的醫療忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.45,0:06:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為了火影 好不容易回到了村子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.75,0:06:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底去哪裡悠閒了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.75,0:06:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火影
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.25,0:06:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是第五代火影
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.55,0:07:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不守承諾真讓人煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.65,0:07:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.75,0:07:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不信呢 騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.05,0:07:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.35,0:07:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方向2 後方50米以內…有7只
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.65,0:07:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是天天嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.25,0:07:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寧次 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.94,0:07:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說那個綱手大人回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.15,0:08:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的哦 你不去看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.55,0:08:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我沒興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.35,0:08:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來有8只啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.95,0:08:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好 綱手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.45,0:08:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊會見大名
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.65,0:08:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再發表繼任第五代火影的宣言
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.65,0:08:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今天起 村子就開始準備繼任儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.35,0:08:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是大名 又是儀式 真夠麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.05,0:08:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.75,0:08:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.55,0:08:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是火影的任務 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.95,0:08:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦間 青葉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發出通告
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.45,0:08:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近幾天內 要讓村裡所有人知道這個消息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.85,0:08:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任命第五代火影的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.15,0:09:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺是個笨蛋 為什麼要死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.55,0:09:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第五代
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.25,0:09:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 肩膀都酸了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.55,0:09:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好喝一杯放鬆一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.88,0:09:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是我想要的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.05,0:09:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.15,0:09:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.75,0:09:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這之前 綱手婆婆還有些事要做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.15,0:09:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說了嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給卡卡西老師 佐助和濃眉看病的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.63,0:09:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.45,0:09:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是鳴人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.75,0:09:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鹿丸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.65,0:09:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.55,0:09:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才該問 你到這裡來幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.45,0:09:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道 老爸讓我來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.05,0:09:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.05,0:09:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了 綱手大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.62,0:09:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是奈良家的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.55,0:10:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有好好照顧鹿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.75,0:10:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡出產的鹿角可是上好的藥材啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.95,0:10:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.35,0:10:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個年紀輕輕 不可一世的傢伙是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.35,0:10:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是新任的火影
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.15,0:10:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然看上去這樣 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.78,0:10:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可她實際上是個50歲的老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.45,0:10:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那後會有期了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.65,0:10:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 去醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.35,0:10:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹿丸 過會兒見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.55,0:10:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你見識一下我的新絕招
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.95,0:10:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人竟然是第五代
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.45,0:10:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好 鹿丸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.65,0:10:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可是這個世上最強而且最美麗的人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.25,0:10:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說她也是三忍中的一點紅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.25,0:10:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火影竟然是個女的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.45,0:10:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正對我來說女人是最麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.05,0:10:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看似個性爽朗 但又很纏人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.45,0:11:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不清楚到底關係處得好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.15,0:11:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概都以為男人會乖乖地聽她們擺佈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.75,0:11:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之就是麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.45,0:11:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹿丸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.18,0:11:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有女人 就沒有男人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.85,0:11:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有女人的話 男人就會變得很沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.85,0:11:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是多麼難纏的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.15,0:11:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對自己喜歡的男人都會表現出溫柔的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.55,0:11:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的倒好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.65,0:11:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸還不是在老媽面前抬不起頭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.85,0:11:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你長大就明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.25,0:11:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 得趕快把正事辦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.55,0:11:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再拖的話 又要被你媽罵了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.65,0:11:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快啊 鹿丸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.46,0:11:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個有了女人也沒用的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.35,0:12:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.75,0:12:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.65,0:12:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.65,0:12:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻 小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.35,0:12:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下就沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.05,0:12:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是帶了個很牛的人回來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.65,0:12:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助這回肯定沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.35,0:12:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.25,0:12:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩朵花
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.55,0:12:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎不是同一天插在這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.25,0:12:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子每天都來探病嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.75,0:12:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從凱老師那裡聽說了您的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.65,0:12:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您無論如何都要治好佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.49,0:12:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.35,0:13:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.75,0:13:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.15,0:13:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.75,0:13:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助 你這傢伙……
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.75,0:14:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人這小子心裡一定很受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.25,0:14:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個 下一個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.19,0:14:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可悲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.75,0:14:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被逃忍二人組傷成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.15,0:14:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來還以為你是個天才呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.65,0:14:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.65,0:14:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 卡卡西老師搞定了 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.98,0:14:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就是濃眉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.95,0:14:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快快快 快去看看我的愛徒小李吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.75,0:14:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小李
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.25,0:14:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.05,0:15:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是你的徒弟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.15,0:15:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 是我最最最關愛的小徒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.75,0:15:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.95,0:15:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.05,0:15:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這種地方無事瞎轉悠好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.56,0:15:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.05,0:15:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和伊魯卡老師約好見面的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.35,0:15:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.45,0:15:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.95,0:15:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.45,0:15:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好慢啊 伊魯卡老師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.45,0:15:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不住對不住
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.85,0:15:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為第五代歸來 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.32,0:15:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有很多工作要做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.95,0:15:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.25,0:15:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.25,0:15:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要開動啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.55,0:15:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.15,0:15:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起當初那個老嚷著要我護額的鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.15,0:15:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你確實成長了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是這麼認為的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.05,0:16:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自打從伊魯卡老師那裡拿到這個護額
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.75,0:16:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經和我非常般配了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.05,0:16:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼呀 又在這裡吹牛了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.95,0:16:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子還早得很呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.15,0:16:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要更努力更活躍才行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.61,0:16:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.35,0:16:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的木葉百廢待興
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.15,0:16:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅是第三代
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.65,0:16:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還損失了很多優秀的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.35,0:16:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實力存留還不到以前的一半
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.65,0:16:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這樣 我們依然要好好完成任務
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.25,0:16:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.65,0:16:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人委託 拒絕掉不就好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.85,0:16:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣當然不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.85,0:16:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們拒絕任務
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.35,0:16:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就等於是向外界宣告我們大不如前了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.35,0:16:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連剛痊癒的卡卡西老師也有任務的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.65,0:16:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.05,0:16:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是形勢嚴峻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.65,0:16:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別一副事不關己的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.15,0:17:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你必須協助綱手大人完成好每一件任務
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.07,0:17:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在此之前 還是填飽肚子最重要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.55,0:17:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是老樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.15,0:17:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.85,0:17:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一碗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.05,0:17:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼時候又…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.15,0:17:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不說廢話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.65,0:17:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要再當忍者了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.25,0:17:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種玩笑就別開了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.75,0:17:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骨頭的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.35,0:17:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散落在重要的神經系統周圍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.35,0:17:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且插在了深處
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.91,0:18:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他這樣的身體是無法執行忍者的任務的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.45,0:18:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說綱手大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.05,0:18:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個笑話實在是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.75,0:18:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算實施手術…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.95,0:18:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再說了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.55,0:18:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙一定是冒充的綱手大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.15,0:18:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許用變身術來欺騙我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.85,0:18:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.65,0:18:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒希望了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.25,0:18:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了我 沒人能做這個手術
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.05,0:18:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花費大量的時間是小事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.35,0:18:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還伴隨著極大的風險
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.55,0:18:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,極大的風險
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.15,0:18:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手術的成功率
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.35,0:18:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最高也就50%
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.85,0:18:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一失敗…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.05,0:18:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.55,0:19:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱老師
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.95,0:19:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決不就此放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.05,0:19:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱老師 這是什麼藥丸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.11,0:19:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在是太苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.65,0:19:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是我特製的青春中藥丸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.95,0:19:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃完一百顆就可以恢復哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.35,0:19:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.35,0:19:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃不完一百顆就不能恢復
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.25,0:19:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不是一天的藥量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.05,0:19:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是放棄當忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.24,0:19:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選擇其他的人生道路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.05,0:19:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小李
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.65,0:20:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小李
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.45,0:20:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.95,0:20:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不讓你幫他診斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.95,0:20:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.15,0:20:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能理解你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.25,0:20:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還是把話說清楚的好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.95,0:20:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些事早晚他都得瞭解的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.35,0:20:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這樣拖下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.85,0:20:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會給他添上一段痛苦的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.70,0:22:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉丸 你該出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.16,0:22:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別煩我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.17,0:22:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 我請你吃拉麵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.57,0:22:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.00,0:22:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 外加蛋和叉燒怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.65,0:22:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的很煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.01,0:22:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這什麼態度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.85,0:22:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可要對你來硬的了 等著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.57,0:22:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.42,0:22:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火之意志的繼承者
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.07,0:23:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一定要看哦
